Tools used:

Ruby: 1.8.7
Rails: 2.3.8
DB: sqlite3
Rails Plugins: mime-types 1.16 (http://mime-types.rubyforge.org), attachment_fu (http://github.com/technoweenie/attachment_fu)
JavaScript: jQuery 1.4.2 (http://jquery.com), uploadify 2.1.0 (http://www.uploadify.com)

Run it:

rake db:schema:load
ruby scripts/server
